{"tid":1807881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[維基百科戰線] 大量區議員條目需要人幫手寫！","createTime":"2020-01-02T04:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T00:32:17.000Z","uid":71237,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"098e70b778362d10348b4a7d2de9ce7e507d0938","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:43:39.000Z","msg":"[維基百科戰線] 大量區議員條目需要人幫手寫！<br />\n<br />\n今屆區議會選舉有大量素人當選，亦有好多組織冒起（例如北炮同盟）。好多有心人喺維基百科撰寫區議員的條目，但係數量龐大，而家人手不足。<br />\n<br />\n需要幫手嘅事項：<br />\n搵返自己區嘅區議員／組織，搜尋有咩新聞報導介紹依啲區議員／組織，區議會有咩最新動態，然後寫落維基百科。<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n1. 用電腦，唔好用手機<br />\n用手機編輯維基百科係極不方便，一定要用電腦。<br />\n2. 註冊帳戶<br />\n唔註冊就會馬上暴露你嘅IP address。其他人有事聯絡你（例如提點有咩地方可以寫好啲）亦比較方便。帳戶名稱最好普通平實啲，唔好同政治抗爭有關，亦唔好比人追查到你現實世界嘅身份。<br />\n3. 無資料唔好格硬寫<br />\n寫維基百科每一句都要有可靠資料來源。就算你親眼目擊嘅事，都唔可以寫落維基百科。每一句都要有新聞報導做基礎，引用資料的方法我下面嘅留言會講。有啲區議員嘅知名度比較低，缺乏新聞報導。依個時候就唔好格硬寫。<br />\n4. 新手可以參考下其他人點寫先，唔好直接寫政綱落去。語調仲要盡量中立，唔好令人一睇就覺得係宣傳。<br />\n例子：<br />\n劉肇軒<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8A%89%E8%82%87%E8%BB%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E8%2582%2587%25E8%25BB%2592&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=a313dc37\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8A%89%E8%82%87%E8%BB%92</a><br />\n劉卓裕<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8A%89%E5%8D%93%E8%A3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E5%258D%2593%25E8%25A3%2595&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=172a2ab4\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8A%89%E5%8D%93%E8%A3%95</a><br />\n延伸閱讀：幫區議員寫維基百科(wiki)前的注意事項<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1755286/page/1 \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1755286/page/1 </a><br />\n<br />\n想搵哂全港區議員，可以睇「2019年香港區議會選舉結果」<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2019%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259E%259C&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=03f5c24a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n維基百科戰線長期需要人手！<br />\n如果發現有嘢值得寫/發現惡意破壞，可以去報料Telegram Bot @wikiscout_Bot 向團隊報告。 <br />\n如果想幫手寫維基百科，可以閱讀新手教學。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1</a><br />\n如果想寫嘢，但又唔知道有咩可以寫，可以睇我們嘅Telegram channel @hkwikichannel ，遇到問題仲可以入Group發問。"},{"pid":"46bd3da088ac731c338dcc9daeb07e10228f3f5f","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"引用資料來源有兩個方法。<br />\n1. 你登記咗account嘅話，可以去setting開啟「視覺化編輯」，跟住就可以用自動工具可以幫你引用來源。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGkGH5P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGkGH5P.gif&h=23d6ce9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過依個方法唔係完美，有啲參數可能會亂咗，可能需要人手執下。<br />\n<br />\n2. 編輯原始碼，你跟依張gif圖直接輸入標題、URL、日期、報章的名稱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b6L0d93.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb6L0d93.gif&h=ba9c7b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 維基百科助手<br />\n依個係一個新嘅工具，可以應付大部分本港的新聞媒體<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NFkHhhIyIJeQEgPZv23biedan_L580EU-4-wKj-qT2M/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1NFkHhhIyIJeQEgPZv23biedan_L580EU-4-wKj-qT2M%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=77589a95\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NFkHhhIyIJeQEgPZv23biedan_L580EU-4-wKj-qT2M/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n你喺黃色格A3輸入新聞報導嘅網址，然後喺黃色格B3輸入新聞報導嘅日期。如果B5至B6能夠成功顯示標題及日期，你直接Copy綠色格B7，再貼落維基百科就可以引用到。<br />\n<br />\n一開始唔熟手唔緊要，總之勇敢試下先。慢慢用熟咗就會進步。"},{"pid":"beb16a3d82e05886184a05a23664fb0d2c30d23c","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:53:44.000Z","msg":"我列一部分需要幫手擴充嘅區議員條目出嚟，希望大家參與。<br />\n<br />\n1. 何偉霖<br />\n何偉霖因管理費事件而知名，亦協助太和邨推翻天價工程。目前條目內序言部分已經有一些資料來源，請根據內容擴寫成一個小章節。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BD%95%E5%81%89%E9%9C%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2581%2589%25E9%259C%2596&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=79629431\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BD%95%E5%81%89%E9%9C%96</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 黃永志<br />\n目前條目的語調並不中立，似連登post多過維基條目。請按照維基百科的方針修改。而且有部分內容沒有可靠來源，需要補充。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E6%B0%B8%E5%BF%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E5%25BF%2597&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=c32f90ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E6%B0%B8%E5%BF%97</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 彭家浩<br />\n其實都有唔少新聞報導都有介紹彭家浩，但目前尚未寫入維基百科。<br />\n詳情可以入Telegram channel @hkwikichannel 睇 <br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BD%AD%E5%AE%B6%E6%B5%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25B5%25A9&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=3f5e218d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BD%AD%E5%AE%B6%E6%B5%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 梁晃維<br />\n同樣有唔少新聞報導都有介紹梁晃維，但目前尚未寫入維基百科。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A2%81%E6%99%83%E7%B6%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%2599%2583%25E7%25B6%25AD&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=2e72047f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A2%81%E6%99%83%E7%B6%AD</a>"},{"pid":"4791e669e0a3a43958e1afc528ed87a769fb4b92","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:55:24.000Z","msg":"維基百科好多嘢你唔寫就無人寫。<br />\n<br />\n林泳淘被TVB解約都係得潦潦一句，無人記錄到底佢發表過咩言論，對被解約有咩睇法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9E%97%E6%B3%B3%E6%B7%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E6%25B7%2598&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=0415c6b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9E%97%E6%B3%B3%E6%B7%98</a>"},{"pid":"dda68b25a64d02c5d6dbc2c5bf8698197509d075","tid":1807881,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:56:35.000Z","msg":"Help push"},{"pid":"ae338d0ea17646b76f7315dc99f7df2ca56318dc","tid":1807881,"uid":188035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"098e70b778362d10348b4a7d2de9ce7e507d0938","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:43:39.000Z","msg":"[維基百科戰線] 大量區議員條目需要人幫手寫！<br />\n<br />\n今屆區議會選舉有大量素人當選，亦有好多組織冒起（例如北炮同盟）。好多有心人喺維基百科撰寫區議員的條目，但係數量龐大，而家人手不足。<br />\n<br />\n需要幫手嘅事項：<br />\n搵返自己區嘅區議員／組織，搜尋有咩新聞報導介紹依啲區議員／組織，區議會有咩最新動態，然後寫落維基百科。<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n1. 用電腦，唔好用手機<br />\n用手機編輯維基百科係極不方便，一定要用電腦。<br />\n2. 註冊帳戶<br />\n唔註冊就會馬上暴露你嘅IP address。其他人有事聯絡你（例如提點有咩地方可以寫好啲）亦比較方便。帳戶名稱最好普通平實啲，唔好同政治抗爭有關，亦唔好比人追查到你現實世界嘅身份。<br />\n3. 無資料唔好格硬寫<br />\n寫維基百科每一句都要有可靠資料來源。就算你親眼目擊嘅事，都唔可以寫落維基百科。每一句都要有新聞報導做基礎，引用資料的方法我下面嘅留言會講。有啲區議員嘅知名度比較低，缺乏新聞報導。依個時候就唔好格硬寫。<br />\n4. 新手可以參考下其他人點寫先，唔好直接寫政綱落去。語調仲要盡量中立，唔好令人一睇就覺得係宣傳。<br />\n例子：<br />\n劉肇軒<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8A%89%E8%82%87%E8%BB%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E8%2582%2587%25E8%25BB%2592&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=a313dc37\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8A%89%E8%82%87%E8%BB%92</a><br />\n劉卓裕<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8A%89%E5%8D%93%E8%A3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E5%258D%2593%25E8%25A3%2595&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=172a2ab4\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8A%89%E5%8D%93%E8%A3%95</a><br />\n延伸閱讀：幫區議員寫維基百科(wiki)前的注意事項<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1755286/page/1 \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1755286/page/1 </a><br />\n<br />\n想搵哂全港區議員，可以睇「2019年香港區議會選舉結果」<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2019%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259E%259C&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=03f5c24a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2019%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n維基百科戰線長期需要人手！<br />\n如果發現有嘢值得寫/發現惡意破壞，可以去報料Telegram Bot @wikiscout_Bot 向團隊報告。 <br />\n如果想幫手寫維基百科，可以閱讀新手教學。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1</a><br />\n如果想寫嘢，但又唔知道有咩可以寫，可以睇我們嘅Telegram channel @hkwikichannel ，遇到問題仲可以入Group發問。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:59:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"926121be6d3cba5b2d2076ccfa2087f49849cb63","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:04:30.000Z","msg":"寫好區議會、區議員條目好重要。<br />\n<br />\n好多人對區議員嘅經歷都一無所知。你將所有介紹過依位區議員嘅資料整理到維基百科，就可以增加大家對佢嘅認識。<br />\n以何偉霖為例，佢曾經抗議富亨邨加管理費，亦幫助過太和邨推翻天價工程。大家只要喺Google搜尋佢個名，維基百科必定喺搜尋結果嘅頭幾位。大家好容易就搵得返佢嘅事跡。<br />\n當你想向其他人介紹何偉霖嘅時候，你未必記得太多詳情，但係你可以隨時上維基睇返。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fc8846f2458f1cefb875fb5328be3c905e958c","tid":1807881,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:07:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"582a076e3d9dfa8a1d3c412212eac3da1c7a522a","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:24:54.000Z","msg":"大家最起碼寫返自己嗰區。"},{"pid":"b0377fb8e522eff6c405b088d4f0c4736c0e97af","tid":1807881,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f1a62e11e1c6a1536d8f0e0dc561c95c97325a","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:06:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47bd7d3c0425c9de61b84ef3ad06369c0a0b8746","tid":1807881,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:38:24.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"840f80435db1e8b7d34c1c572373024a9ee2d933","tid":1807881,"uid":167578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5c28a8aa4f2fbe861a9cf61efd4e2e9e51bd88","tid":1807881,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:47:30.000Z","msg":"1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9e25972180b1b5adb8316d95faa3e0d7aa0194","tid":1807881,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:50:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7bdf84cae08233fa16b725c73ceb9adb5952a80e","tid":1807881,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:53:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"26371f4be77c2a10745b85aa1dd734fa34525a31","tid":1807881,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:53:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[隨筆新詩]黎明前 光復後<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789990</a>"},{"pid":"2c5b26cc0f9aa842c5470fec3a5280dd6df066c4","tid":1807881,"uid":286700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"Push 超有用"},{"pid":"a6dcc4a3491f05fa979a9345d245879839f4bff0","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"比多啲優質嘅例子大家睇。<br />\n荃民議政<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E6%B0%91%E8%AD%B0%E6%94%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=51a6df5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E6%B0%91%E8%AD%B0%E6%94%BF</a><br />\n<br />\n青衣島民<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%9D%92%E8%A1%A3%E5%B3%B6%E6%B0%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%259D%2592%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E6%25B0%2591&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=bbdb4743\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%9D%92%E8%A1%A3%E5%B3%B6%E6%B0%91</a>"},{"pid":"da299dc16686e380fe88eedf7e0d570cfa00a443","tid":1807881,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:13:24.000Z","msg":"PUsh"},{"pid":"daad435f36c8f4a372b2f103c7b81764713e113e","tid":1807881,"uid":74783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:07:14.000Z","msg":"大推"},{"pid":"3b241a284141c07e075321e3d96c4b0e893c3895","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:05:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2a3b468e7a62e23cb5ee6ef50caac56940d6f89","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f76d4d9ce5bfe76591f7480a120bc6dc68939bf5","tid":1807881,"uid":210608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T14:14:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bbf2290313f3d9f86aeace2aeb9648b906d1410","tid":1807881,"uid":341560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n一陣試下去搞 (感覺有D似做通識科IES咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"a33ff250e93029332ba9666bb88628737e7a3375","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dd985db917d96a2ed6c9bc3d822eb1f109f6742","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"771f49ac42cf8956e75e5d8f78c48547e6d15f08","tid":1807881,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T16:01:57.000Z","msg":"民主派內無專業人仕幫?"},{"pid":"0c16e6a3b2e826a8021a36afdb0cf2a2a1eb10de","tid":1807881,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T18:33:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5845939f15e8b0bafa9a226c310eb1b92af7da92","tid":1807881,"uid":129042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T18:39:45.000Z","msg":"南區撚揮手準備做"},{"pid":"a05aacaec07885c654d06ff6cf351f41a0643b98","tid":1807881,"uid":19617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T18:47:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da801d1ed139d993824888344d9d396517a2639","tid":1807881,"uid":3